OL,3,CSister remembers teenage brother
OL,4,Ckilled in Omagh atrocity
OL,6,FA teenage boy killed in the Omagh bomb
OL,7,Fhas been remembered by his sister as
OL,8,F"radiating light".
OL,10,FThe sister of Alan Radford, 16,
OL,11,Fdescribed him as having "no malice,
OL,12,Fnot a bad bone in his body".
OL,14,FClaire Hayes gave an emotional tribute
OL,15,Fto her brother at the Omagh Bombing
OL,16,FInquiry in the Co Tyrone town on the
OL,17,Fsecond day of commemorative statements
OL,18,Fto the 29 victims and those affected.
