OL,3,CSister remembers teenage brother
OL,4,Ckilled in Omagh atrocity
OL,6,FMs Hayes described her brother as
OL,7,Fbeing full of "immense love" with a
OL,8,F"caring nature".
OL,10,F"It's like he was the ray of sunshine,
OL,11,Fthe light just shone out of that boy,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,F"He had the purest heart, heart of
OL,15,Fgold and the clarity and innocence he
OL,16,Fhad was like the purest form of a
OL,17,Fdiamond you could ever get.
